headline: Raymond James Ltd. Recruitment Momentum Continues as the Edmonton Branch Welcomes Lance Priemaza
summary: Raymond James Ltd., Canada's largest independent financial services firm, is pleased to welcome Assistant Branch Manager & Financial Advisor Lance Priemaza to the firm's Edmonton Branch.
